CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 21, 1962, pg. 21, reads: "Winning Team - Members of the winning South All-Star team are shown after they defeated the North team in first annual Tri-Borough League All-Star Game at Ammon Field last week. Left to right, standing: Irene Robinson, Carol White, Patty Carter, Sandra White and Ruth Chance.  Kneeling: Carol Wilson, Mary Conyers and Elizabeth Moorefield.  Rear: Walter Robinson, manager and Ruby Huddeleston. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: South All-Star team softball players from Homewood Orbits and "Satilites," squatting from left: Carol Wilson, Mary Conyers, Elizabeth Moorefield; standing: Irene Robinson, manager Walter Robinson, Carol White, Patty Carter, Ruby Huddleston, Sandra White, and Ruth Chance
